trans-unit.source: Represents a hash set that mutates with little or no memory allocations and that can produce or build on immutable hash set instances very efficiently.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta un set di hash che viene modificato con allocazioni di memoria minime o nulle e in grado di produrre o compilare su istanze di set di hash non modificabili in modo molto efficiente.

trans-unit.source: **NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)
trans-unit.target: **Pacchetto NuGet**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">informazioni sulle raccolte non modificabili e su come installarle</see>)

trans-unit.source: Although <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet%601.Union%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and other methods already provide fast bulk change operations on a collection, the <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet%601.Builder> class allows multiple combinations of changes to be made to a set with equal efficiency.
trans-unit.target: Sebbene <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet%601.Union%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> e altri metodi forniscono già le operazioni di modifica di massa veloce su una raccolta, la <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet%601.Builder> classe consente a più combinazioni di modifiche da apportare a un set con efficienza uguale.
